          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-469-07H1-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-469-07H1-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-469-07H1-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">A</hi>N ass's hoof alone can hold</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-2" n="2">That pois'nous juice, which kills by cold.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-3" n="3">Methought, when I this poem read,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-4" n="4">No vessel but an ass's head</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-5" n="5">Such frigid fustian could contain;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-6" n="6">I mean the head without the brain.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-7" n="7">The cold conceits, the chilling thoughts</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-8" n="8">Went down like stupifying draughts:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-9" n="9">I found my head began to swim,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-10" n="10">A numbness crept thro' ev'ry limb.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-11" n="11">In haste with imprecations dire,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-12" n="12">I threw the volume in the fire:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-13" n="13">When who could think, tho' cold as ice,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-14" n="14">It burnt to ashes in a trice.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-15" n="15"><lb/>How could I more enhance its fame?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-07H1-line-16" n="16">Tho' born in snow, it dy'd in flame.</l>
          </lg>
